	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hang out by the west gate in FP and auction for SoW's and binds. Alot of high levels are very grateful for this type of service, especially if you're willing to come find them because they're KoS in the city. You can do pretty well doing that - and while it won't make you wealthy, it will definitely help you get some better equipment. <br>My stronget advice to you, though - is level like crazy. Try to change your focus (at least for now) from getting stuff to getting xp. Money comes ALOT more easily in the mid 20s than it ever will in the teens. Trust me, your level will make an enormous difference. At lvl 24 solo forest giants in Warsliks woods and at level 27 group in crypt of Dalnir. You'll be pretty set pretty quickly.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
