<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=96960686832166></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96960686832166><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96960686832166>Soloing Tips, Anyone?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96960686832166#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=1725><span id= >Ganaleno</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Sep 22nd 3:14 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm a druid on the Solusek Ro server, and just made lvl 26.&nbsp;&nbsp;I'd like to know where would be the best places/npc's to solo are (for xp and/or loot).  Also, I've heard that us Druids can solo Giants, but haven't seen any info at which giants can be solo'ed at what levels.  Any information is GREATLY appreciated. <br><br>Ganaleno<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>
<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=96964786616663></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96964786616663><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96964786616663><sorry for the double post> (n/t)</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96964786616663#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=759><span id=Scholar>Adiemus</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>63 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Sep 22nd 2:37 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.15]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
