<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=96936866921270></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96936866921270><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96936866921270>Druid soloing</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96936866921270#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Sep 19th 9:04 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Heya all.&nbsp;&nbsp;I was just wondering where the best place is to solo for a level 10 Druid.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
