	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok speaking as a level 43 druid..<br>I pretty much solo'd at a few different places<br>--<br>You can either partner with someone of equal level in teh Butcher block on the dwarf spawns such as the graveyard (2 spawn) use harmony and pull one snared and nuked into oblivion rinse and repeat or a Signus a single spawn near the BB bandit camp.<br>--<br>Lower Guk Bedroom or even Assassin/supplier room <br>in a group, its tough competition vs them clerics.<br>so dont compete with them work your other strengths, snaring, dotting and back up healing!<br>so you can copmpete with the wizards,necros and shaman slots.<br>--<br>Cazic Thule<br>The sewers in a group, AoF, or especially 4 corners or 4C this is the ground level around the Archon temple.&nbsp;&nbsp;plenty of lizards here, around 31ish 2 per corner plus a couple roamers and you can pull from the first or second level of the temple relatively easily also.<br>---<br>                 *************<br>Most preferred however is The Overthere!<br>The signle most positive zone for druids, there are areas here that are high 20's to low 30's.<br>the tactic here is either to charm/befriend a Kunark rhino or Sabretooth Tigress (beware the tiger will break loose too fast)  you can then sick your pet on a nearby speculant (cactus), or cockatrice.  The aggro radius is very very small,<br>I have had mobs walk by my sitting/medding form 8 out of 10 times without aggroing me, however just becareful. <br><br> Now the charm, pls have charisma gear, a good charisma is 110 if u can get it that high.  Charisma bracers +7 each. Silk evening tunic +5, crude stien +15, Order of thunder +5, and drake hide leggings +5 are all very easy to acquire. thats +44 charisma with a base 75 is plenty.  <br>---<br>you can also fear/kite witha pet makes it very nice. if your target is a tigress, tiger or rhino these can be terrorized/ensnared which will allow your pet to kick but whil it slowly follows the poor mob.  <br>---<br>on a good run I have killed and recvd exp for 8 mobs with charm/fear kite for ONE FULL BAR of MANA!.<br>---<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
