	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sometimes, mobs just WON'T be taunted onto the tank.&nbsp;&nbsp;They decide they are going to have Druid for dinner.  <br><br>I don't know about you, but I'd rather not be a froggie dinner.  Mem root. When the mob jumps you, stand still, root it, and walk away.  This works even on summoning mobs.  Just don't forget to snare when root breaks.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
